        <div type="letter">
        <opener><dateline><date when="1918-04-26">April 26, 1918.<dateline></date><salute>Dear <persName key="harriet_monroe">Harriet</persName>:-</salute>
        </opener>
         <p>This note will be forwarded to you by my friend, <persName key="florence_ayscough">Mrs. Francis Ayscough</persName>. I want you to meet, and if <place key="chicago">Chicago</place> is as kind to her is it has always been to me, she has a very pleasant time to look forward to.</p>
         <closure>Affectionately yours,</closure>
        </div>
